OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cawarded honorary degree
OL,6,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015, as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,Fsystem made it appear as though money
OL,11,Fwas missing at their branches.
OL,13,FAddressing the students at the
OL,14,Fgraduation ceremony, he said: "One of
OL,15,Fthe things the Post Office scandal
OL,16,Fshows quite vividly is that things go
OL,17,Fwrong.
OL,19,F"But when things go wrong don't cover
OL,20,Fit up - because the cover-up can be
OL,21,Fworse than the crime."
