OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cawarded honorary degree
OL,6,FSir Alan had been running the post
OL,7,Foffice in his shop in Craig-y-Don,
OL,8,Fnear Llandudno, for years without any
OL,9,Fissue.
OL,11,FBut shortly after the Horizon
OL,12,Faccounting system was introduced,
OL,13,Finexplicable discrepancies began to
OL,14,Fappear.
OL,16,FDespite multiple complaints to the
OL,17,FPost Office about the reliability of
OL,18,Fthe new system, in 2003, Sir Alan's
OL,19,Fcontract was terminated without reason.
