OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cawarded honorary degree
OL,6,FThe termination meant forfeiting his
OL,7,Finvestment of over #60,000- which was
OL,8,Fa significant sum to their retail shop.
OL,10,FSir Alan founded the Justice For
OL,11,FSubpostmasters Alliance in 2009 which
OL,12,Fled to convictions against postmasters
OL,13,Fbeing quashed, and the launch of the
OL,14,Fongoing Post Office inquiry.
OL,16,FHowever, he made clear in his speech
OL,17,Fthat the "battle is still ongoing",
OL,18,Fand the fight for justice is "not over
OL,19,Fyet."
